	dprr:hasNoteText "14 As Perpennia's father, M. Perperna, Cos. 92, Cens. 86, had by 69 attained the age of 78, she had probably begun her service as a Vestal many years earlier, perhaps before 100 B. C. See below, on Fonteia." .
